snippet.title: PARADISE ® | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Add us to your Wishlist:
🎮 STEAM - https://store.steampowered.com/app/3281420/Paradise/
🎮 Epic Games Store・https://store.epicgames.com/en-US/p/paradise-57edc7

Welcome to PARADISE ®, the revolutionary new development from Ultra Games Limited. This groundbreaking project merges a dynamic social platform with the first AI game, creating an all-encompassing ecosystem. 

It is a game that combines elements of GTA and SIMS, as well as advanced technology.

Watch our latest trailer to see how PARADISE® is setting new standards in gaming.

🌏 Website・https://paradisevs.com/
🌐 (X) Twitter・https://x.com/paradisevscom

Song: Busy Earnin’
Artist: Jungle
Written by: Joshua Lloyd-Watson, Tom McFarland
Published by: Universal Music Publishing Group on behalf of Beggars Music
Courtesy of: XL Recordings
